'''Alidu Seidu''' (born 4 June 2000) is a Ghanaian-French<ref>{{Cite web |last=Demba |first=Varore |date=24 April 2024 |title=Alidu Seidu : "Depuis tout petit, j'ai baigné dans la culture ghanéenne" - Football |url=https://sportnewsafrica.com/news-football/montpellier-modibo-sagnan-depuis-tout-petit-jai-baigne-dans-la-culture-malienne/ |access-date=7 August 2025 |website=Sport News Africa |language=fr-FR}}</ref> professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for French {{French football updater|Rennes}} club [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]] and the [[Ghana national football team|Ghana national team]].

==Club career==
On 1 June 2019, Seidu joined [[Clermont Foot]] from the [[JMG Academy]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jmgmanagement.pro/2017/12/01/alidu-seidu-jmg-academician-profesionnal-player/|title=C.S. Clermont sign Alidu Seidu|publisher=Soccer News|date=1 June 2019|access-date=18 September 2020|archive-date=23 September 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923114407/http://jmgmanagement.pro/2017/12/01/alidu-seidu-jmg-academician-profesionnal-player/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He made his debut with Clermont in a 1–1 [[Ligue 2]] draw with [[Toulouse FC]] on 19 September 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Clermont vs. Toulouse - 19 September 2020 - Soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/09/19/france/ligue-2/clermont-foot-auvergne/toulouse-fc/3287847/|access-date=28 November 2020|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ligue 2 : retrouvez les temps forts du match Clermont Foot - Toulouse FC (1-1)|url=https://france3-regions.francetvinfo.fr/auvergne-rhone-alpes/puy-de-dome/clermont-ferrand/ligue-2-suivez-direct-match-du-clermont-foot-63-face-toulouse-1875418.html|access-date=28 November 2020|website=France 3 Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes|date=19 September 2020 |language=fr-FR}}</ref>

On 29 January 2024, Seidu signed a contract with [[Stade Rennais F.C.|Rennes]] until 2028.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Rennes|url=https://www.staderennais.com/actualites/equipe-pro/alidu-seidu-officiellement-rennais|title=Alidu Seidu officiellement Rennais !|trans-title=Alidu Seidu officially at Rennes!|date=29 January 2024|access-date=29 January 2024|language=fr}}</ref>

